</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2015 08:42:43 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/6185/how-do-i-create-a-desktop-wallpaper-slideshow/</guid></item><item><title>Answer by SpicyCat for &lt;p&gt;How do I create a desktop wallpaper slideshow with my own set of images?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;With the images coming from a pictures folder, or pre-selected&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;With the images displayed in order, or randomly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;With the images changing every few minutes, or after random periods of time&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
